<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.1">
<l>āycciya raḻaippa veṇṇeyuṇ ṭorukā lālilai vaḷarntavem perumāṉ</l>
<l>pēycciyai mulaiyuṇ ṭiṇaimaru tiṟuttup perunila maḷantavaṉ kōyil</l>
<l>kāyttanīḷ kamukuṅ kataliyun teṅku meṅkumām poḻilkaḷi ṉaṭuvē</l>
<l>vāyttanīr pāyum maṇṇiyiṉ teṉpāl tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple of the one who measured the vast land,</l>
<l rend="indent">having eaten from the breast of the demoness</l>
<l rend="indent">and broken the joined marutu [trees],</l>
<l>Our great lord who slept on a banyan leaf one time, having eaten ghee</l>
<l rend="indent">so the herdess cried out,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi on the southern side of the Maṇṇi [River]</l>
<l rend="indent">where copious water flows everywhere</l>
<l>Midst groves of fruited tall areca, banana, and coconut [trees]</l>
<l rend="indent">that are everywhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
